</p><p>
Lalle wannan tsarin amai kewaye ko mai maimaita kansa yana taimakawa 
matuka a wajen sanya manhaja ta rin kamaimaita aikin ta har sau wani
Adadi mai yawa domin aiwatar da wani umarni. Sannan yana taimakawa a 
Wajen takaice layikan umarni masu yawazuwalayikayankadanyayingina
