manhajar,tokuwagyararzaikasanceneawajegudakawaikumabatare
daanshawatawahalasosaiba.Wannankewayawarkomaimaituwada
manhajarkeyitadalilinamfanidalayinumarnigudashiakekiradasuna
'Looping'afanninharsunankirikira(programminglanguages),kumaabune
sananneawannanfanni.Ire-irentsarimaikewayekomaimaimaitakansa
yakasukashibiyu;sune:tsarimaikewayemaiamfanidasharadinka'ida
(conditional),dakumatsarimaikewayemaiamfanidasharadin'counter'.
Dukkansuwadannantsarikanzamuyidubiacikinsuawannanbabinin
Allahyayarda.
