1)Tsarimaikewayekomaimaitakansamaiamfanidasharadincounter
(conter-controlledloop).
Awannantsarinmaikewayen,manhajarzaidingakewayowanesannanya
rinkakarakorage1asharadinka'idardaakasakamishisannanalokaci
gudakumayanaaunasharadinka'idardayakekaruwakoraguwaridanta
</p><p>
wuceadadinsharadinka'idadaakeso,tosaiyadakatardaaikinmanhajar
anankokumayashigakarantawasulayikanumarnidabasudaalakada
wannantsarimaikewayen,ammaidanyakarakoyarage1sannanyaauna
saibaikaisharadinka'idardaakasakamishiba,tosaiyabaraikin
manhajaryasakekewayoyawa,hakazaiyitayiharsaiyacimmabukata.A
kowaccekewayowayanakiyayesharadindaakayimasakarikoragina
baya.Ma'anaidansharadinka'idaryanarikeda1nedazu,tosaiyakara
masa1tokagakuwasabonsharadinka'idaryazama2kenan.Tokuwa
wannan2shinetsarimaikewayena'counter'zaikiyayeamatsayinsabon
sharadinka'ida.
Wannantsarinamaikewayekomaimaimaitakansana'counter'yanada
bangaroriharguda4.Sune:
➡ Gurbinkaddaramafarinka'ida(initializationstage):Wannangurbine
daakekaddarafarkonlambakoharafindaakesoyazamasharadinka'ida
nafarkodazaifaraaiwatardaumarnidaakabashi.Misaliamisalinmuna
Haidarzaikaddaramafarinlambarsharadinka'idarneda1watoamadadin
ranarLitinin.
➡ Gurbinaunasharadinka'ida(Testcondition):Wannankumagurbineda
zaidingaaunasabonsharadinka'idakafinyabarmanhajaryasake
kewayowa,bambancinsadagurbinkaddaramafarinsharadinka'idashine;
shigurbinkaddaramafarinsharadinka'idasaudayakawaimanhajarke
karantashiafarkodominfaraaikinaiwatardaumarnindaakasakamasa,
ammashiwannantsarinabiyunagurbinaunasharadinka'ida(Test
condition)shine;akowaccekewayowadamanhajarkeyisaiyakaranta
taredaaunasabonsharadinka'idarkafinnanyabadadamaraiwatarda
umarnindaketaredawannanka'idar,sabodahakayayindasabon
sharadinka'idayazarceadadindaakasakamasaakesonkaryawucena
yawankewayowadaakesoyayiyayingudanarmanhajartokuwasaikaga
manhajaryadakatadaganan.
Atakaicedai,awannanbangarenabiyunaikinmanhajazaicigabada
aiwatuwanematukarsaiidanamsarsharadinka'idarkayazamtoE(True)
ammayayindaakasamuyazamaA'a(False)toaikinmanhajarzaidakata.
</p><p>
