2)Tsarimaikewayowadafarkokafinfaraamfanidasharadinka'ida:A
wannantsarin,manhajarzaifaraaiwatardaumarnindaakasakamishine
farkosannansaiyafarala'akaridasharadinka'idakafinyasakekewayowa.
Saiyatabbatardacewaramsarsharadinka'idarkatazamantoEne(True)
dominyasakekewayowaidanbahakabakuwabazaikewayobazai
dakata.Shiwannantsarinnatsarimaikewayemaiamfanidasharadin
ka'ida,yafila'akaridafarkonsharadinka'idasamadaadadinyawan
</p><p>
kewayowardazaiyi.
Ayayinamfanidawannantsarinabiyun,akwaikalmomiguda3wandanda
kowanneanaiyaamfanidashiawajentsarawannantsari.Sune;'While',
'Dowhile'dakuma'Dountil'.
</p><p>
Kalmar'While'
Wannan kalmaramfaninsashineyarinkasanyaaikin manhajayana
zagayowakomaimaituwabataredaansanyamasaadadindaakesoya
tsayaba,kawaidaidolenefarkonsharadinka'idarkayakasanceEne(True)
kafinmanhajaryasakekewayowaammayayindasharadinyajuyazuwa
A'a(False),tokuwamanhajarzaidakatadagakewayendayakeyi.
Bakamarakalmar'for'damukayibayaniabayabaindashiwannankalma
na'while'yakedabangarebiyukawai,sune;bangarenfarkoshinegurbin
sharadinka'ida.Wannanbangare shinemanhajarkeaunawafarkodomin
sanincewakosharadindaakesoyacikashi(True)kokuwaa'a(False)
kafinyashigafaraaikinkewayowa.Sannanbangarenabiyukumashine
asalingundarinumarnindaakasanyamasadayaaiwatarkumashinezai
yitamaimaitashisauwasuadadimasuyawasabaninkalmar'for'daake
sanyamasasharadinfarawadakumasharadindakatarwa.
GakadandagamisalinyaddamanhajarHaidartakeidanzamuyiamfanida
kalmar'while'.
